  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Comfort Twin Rooms</strong> have recently been re-furbished and are about 17m² and sleep two or three people. They have south-facing views towards the Val Sapin, TV, minibar, tea &amp; coffee making facilities, safe, bath, shower and hairdryer.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Twin Rooms </strong>have also been re-furbished and are larger than Comfort rooms at about 18m². They sleep up to three people (extra bed is a single bed). Superior rooms have views of Mont Blanc.</p>
<p><strong>Executive Rooms </strong>are about 22m² and sleep up to three people (extra bed is a single sofa bed). They have a private whirlpool on the terrace with views of Mont Blanc. These rooms are only available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Twin rooms for single use</strong> are about 14m². They have a queen size bed and are South facing.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
